15 maiden lane is a 1936 american crime film directed by allan dwan and starring claire trevor and cesar romero , with lloyd nolan .   the plot involves an insurance investigator ( trevor ) who infiltrates a gang who had stolen jewels from the eponymous building on maiden lane in the fulton street district of manhattan .   the neighborhood had been the center of new york city 's diamond district since the 19th century before its gradual relocation uptown to 47th street after world war ii .   the museum of modern art in new york city screened a restored print of the film in june 2013 as part of an allan dwan retrospective .